title: Beat a plat 3!! I'm silver 4!!!
body:
WOOO HOO

I don't usually get excited for a win or a loss, but I thought this zed platinum 3 player was going to trash me! I didn't do amazing at first, going 1-1 with him, and then got ganked like a dummy by shaco, but in the end I was kicking ass!!!!!
YeaAHHYAA
